## ADR Process

### Template (docs/adr/YYYYMMDD-title.md)
```
# Status
Proposed | Accepted | Deprecated | Superseded by ADR-XXX

# Context
Why is this decision needed?

# Decision
The choice made.

# Consequences
Trade-offs, positive/negative effects.
```

### Guidelines
- One ADR per significant architectural decision.
- Include alternatives considered and reasoning.
- Link ADR from affected README/docs.
- Review ADRs every 12 months for relevance.
